    "description": "<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-64d3f256-7fff-b002-69be-a787624054c1\" dir=\"ltr\">Finally, at 6th level you have learned to direct some of the power of your curse outward. What form this takes depends on your Artifact Affliction:</p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Unmoored:</strong> You can cast @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.05w9nzp0kvu94k3h]{Mirror Image} without using a spell slot once per long rest.</li><li dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Paranoid:</strong> You can cast @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.i7sh0e2wqmql4cac]{See Invisibility} without using a spell slot once per long rest.</li><li dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Troubled:</strong> You can cast @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.36x8lw8mhfigm7ti]{Enthrall} without using a spell slot once per long rest.</li><li dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Fettered:</strong> You can cast @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.9mdbn49lbvsc3r01]{Deadweight} without using a spell slot once per long rest.</li><li dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Gravebound:</strong> You can cast @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.9eojtnhu5ptcipov]{Ray of Enfeeblement} without using a spell slot once per long rest.</li></ul>",
